describe main looks very much like some sort of brigand, or bandit. All in all, not someone who looks like you want to meet him in a dark alley, or pretty much anywhere for that matter.

describe zone head clear
describe zone hair His hair is like midnight - black but with a subtle shine of blue as the light hits it.
describe zone eyes $NEW_LINE$His eyes are a deep emerald green, and his stare is somewhat disconcerting.
describe zone face $NEW_LINE$His face is seemingly locked in a scowl, even when he's not angry. And pale. Too pale. Corpse-like. He even has a blue tinge to his lips.
describe zone neck His neck has a strange scar across it. Or is it a bruise?
describe zone arms His arms are athletic, muscular but not rippling. A selection of faded tattoos adorn them.
describe zone legs His legs are athletic, muscular but not rippling.
describe zone hands His hands have a patchwork of scars and cuts across them, a hazard of his profession no doubt.
describe zone feet He has rather large feet.
describe zone back clear
describe zone chest $NEW_LINE$He's quite slim built, torso-wise. And again, you notice just how pale his skin is.
describe zone abdomen clear

